  "name": "Rubber Band Generator",
  "description": "This is the generator section to go with the rubber band motor which can be found here\r\n\r\nyou can find a video about this here https://youtu.be/6lrnD_-gFsY\r\n\r\nand to finish it you will need 2 x bearings 22mm by 8mm by 7mm, 36 circular neodymium  magnets 10mm by 1mm an some magnet wire in the range of 0.2mm to 0.05mm - any is good but the thin stuff is hard to handle - the thinner the wire the more turns you can get in the space so the higher the voltage - wind a serpentine coil with as much wire as will fit in the cassette\r\n\r\nyou will also need to build the rubber band motor and the files for that can be found here: https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:6784387",
